cz.cesnet.cloud.occi

Class Model

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.cesnet.cloud.occi.Model

  • public class Model
extends Object
    Class representing an OCCI model. Can contain instances of classes Kind, Mixin and Action.
    Author:
    Michal Kimle
